<h1 id="toc0"><span>个人比较满意的作品</span></h1>
<div class="list-pages-box">    

<h2><span><a href="/scp-cn-075">SCP-CN-075</a> - <strong>为了基金会！</strong> +181/-9=172</span></h2>
<p>关于铁血、忠诚与英魂。<br />
入坑第一作，创意来自于<span class="error-inline"><em>Alex Stevenson</em> 不匹配任何一个现有的用户名</span>的草稿<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><em><span class="ruby">自虚无中迈来的战士们，尽着最后的职责<span class="rt">Warriors rised from void, finishing their last duty.</span></span></em></p>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    

<h2><span><a href="/scp-cn-984">SCP-CN-984</a> - <strong>87%</strong> +51/-12=39</span></h2>
<p>关于当硬币正反面朝上的几率都为87%时。<br />
重写自<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/apmv" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3550607); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3550607&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610245719" alt="#ApmV" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3550607)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/apmv" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3550607); return false;">#ApmV</a></span>的作品<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><em><span class="ruby">87%，我们赢的概率。<span class="rt">87 percent, our chance for victory.</span></span></em></p>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    

<h2><span><a href="/scp-cn-1539">SCP-CN-1539</a> - <strong>登高朝圣</strong> +36/-3=33</span></h2>
<p>关于向往山峦的人们到底在追求什么。<br />
由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/leooverheat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3007237); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3007237&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610245719" alt="LeoOverheat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3007237)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/leooverheat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3007237); return false;">LeoOverheat</a></span>提供原始创意<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><em><span class="ruby">胡为乎遑遑欲何之？<span class="rt">YRU guys in such a hurry?</span></span></em></p>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    

<h2><span><a href="/scp-cn-116-ex">SCP-CN-116-EX</a> - <strong>烨活的遗物</strong> +204/-15=189</span></h2>
<p>关于忒休斯、中文屋，以及挚爱可触及地离去。<br />
写给<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/novichok" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3995050); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3995050&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610245719" alt="NOVICHOK" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3995050)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/novichok" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3995050); return false;">NOVICHOK</a></span><br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><em><span class="ruby">“谢谢你的陪伴。”<span class="rt">&quot;Thanks for accompany.&quot;</span></span></em></p>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div>
<h1 id="toc1"><span>仍可改进的作品</span></h1>
<div class="list-pages-box">    

<h2><span><a href="/the-last-moment">机娘的噩梦</a> +236/-30=206</span></h2>
<p>关于自我意识、陪伴与救赎。<br />
与<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xiao-lin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3711439); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3711439&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610245719" alt="Xiao Lin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3711439)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xiao-lin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3711439); return false;">Xiao Lin</a></span>的合著，写给[数据损坏]<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><em><span class="ruby">“也谢谢你。”<span class="rt">&quot;You did it well.&quot;</span></span></em></p>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    

<h2><span><a href="/scp-cn-1002">SCP-CN-1002</a> - <strong>深空的太平间</strong> +166/-5=161</span></h2>
<p>关于辉煌、遗赠与不灭的信念。<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><em><span class="ruby">“它在等着我们。”<span class="rt">&quot;It's waiting for us.&quot;</span></span></em></p>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    

<h2><span><a href="/last-order">最终之作</a> +213/-8=205</span></h2>
<p>关于雕像的里面到底装着什么。<br />
与<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/old-wall" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2742867); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2742867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610245720" alt="Old wall" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2742867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/old-wall" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2742867); return false;">Old wall</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rye-travis" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3290685); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3290685&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610245720" alt="Rye Travis" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3290685)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rye-travis" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3290685); return false;">Rye Travis</a></span>和<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-wengwan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3449998); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3449998&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610245720" alt="Dr-wengwan" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3449998)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-wengwan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3449998); return false;">Dr-wengwan</a></span>合著完成。<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><em><span class="ruby">“回去粘上！”<span class="rt">&quot;Stick them back!&quot;</span></span></em></p>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    

<h2><span><a href="/scp-cn-627">SCP-CN-627</a> - <strong><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">圣甲虫秘境</span> 甲虫神</strong> +33/-3=30</span></h2>
<p>关于生存、蔑视与因果轮。<br />
用于背景设定<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><em><span class="ruby">“神明听不见我们的悲呼的。”<span class="rt">&quot;The God can't hear our begging.&quot;</span></span></em></p>
</div>

    
    
    
    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    

<h2><span><a href="/scp-cn-748">SCP-CN-748</a> - <strong>最高意志</strong> +26/-4=22</span></h2>
<p>关于进化、涅槃与异常。<br />
